freenet.client.async
Class InsertCompressor

java.lang.Object
  freenet.client.async.InsertCompressor
All Implemented Interfaces:
CompressJob
public class InsertCompressor
extends Object
implements CompressJob

Compress a file in order to insert it. This class acts as a tag in the database to ensure that inserts are not forgotten about, and also can be run on a non-database thread from an executor.
